The genius of Netflix's Daredevil can be summed up in one scene. In the closing minutes of Episode 2, "Cut Man," Matt Murdock (Charlie Cox) breaches a Russian mob den to rescue a missing boy. This sets off a three-minute, single-shot fight sequence in which Daredevil brutally takes on an entire gang of villains. The fight leaves Matt victorious, but also exhausted, bloody, and bruised.

I spoke to Daredevil's stunt coordinator Philip Silvera
